title: Le Doggy Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Take-out
description: A vegetarian cafe that welcomes both humans and dogs alike. Specializes in veggie burgers and house-made cakes and desserts. Enjoy your food with your dog by your side. It is a unique place where customers could feel comfortable to start conversations with other patrons and share common experiences. Opened Jan 2015.
